  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Facility Specialist (Cleaning)",
  "description": "<p>We are seeking a detail-oriented and proactive <strong>Facility Specialist</strong> to oversee cleaning operations across various client sites. The ideal candidate will ensure that all cleaning services meet high-quality standards, comply with safety regulations, and are delivered efficiently.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Oversee day-to-day cleaning operations of our clients</li><li>Conduct site inspections to ensure compliance with cleanliness, hygiene, and safety standards.</li><li>Manage cleaning teams, assign duties, and provide on-the-job training.</li><li>Develop and implement cleaning schedules, ensuring timely completion of tasks.</li><li>Monitor the usage and inventory of cleaning supplies, equipment, and chemicals.</li><li>Liaise with clients to understand their specific cleaning requirements and address any concerns.</li><li>Ensure adherence to workplace safety regulations and best practices.</li><li>Collaborate with vendors for procurement and maintenance of cleaning equipment.</li><li>Assist in project management for large-scale cleaning assignments, including high-rise and façade cleaning.</li><li>Maintain records of cleaning activities, inspections, and staff performance.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Proven experience in the cleaning or facility management industry.</li><li>Strong knowledge of cleaning techniques, equipment, and chemicals.</li><li>Ability to manage and lead cleaning teams effectively.</li><li>Good understanding of workplace safety regulations.</li><li>Good communication skills to interact with clients and staff.</li></ul>",
